{"tid":1454258,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戰友們，聽我講，請繼續喺你自己既行業發光發熱","createTime":"2019-08-12T06:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T07:03:56.000Z","uid":183649,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"db640ae6e1fac6f70969fb9eb9da5db5381bf812","tid":1454258,"uid":183649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:48:31.000Z","msg":"我知呢一刻講呢啲野唔啱聽<br />\n我都好心痛，好辛苦。但我想盡力講我的見解<br />\n<strong>用盡力量，如同革命既力量喺你地既行業做到最好，上位，但毋忘初心</strong><br />\n<br />\n點解? 梁天琦都有講，革命未必在短時間內完成<br />\n<br />\n各位發完夢，都係要返工的。無辦法的，資本主義社會總係有hierarchy的，在上者總係有多啲權力的<br />\n<br />\n簡單如保安行業，你估放警入黎果下，保安員有say 定保安主任有say?<br />\n做HR既，你估director 定hr officer對罷工有say?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另一個角度，你想藍絲做你呀頭定你做佢呀頭?</span><br />\n再另一方面，俗世上錢真係好重要，你要黎課金又好咩都好<br />\n<br />\n我知道以上說話不合時宜<br />\n但都係重要的，唔講權力，講技能，你做到上位acquire 更多工作上既技能，光復後既香港你就可以付出更多去服務社會。make a better world, 唔係正正係我地既初衷咩?<br />\n<br />\n我知好辛苦，但改變世界一直唔係易事，各位加油。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc08e16fc6982d175fad60ca7502c56613f2c0a7","tid":1454258,"uid":249376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:49:40.000Z","msg":"咁我諗你要推到2047先搞得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61eb7d298c13685db5e01ba5afa183afe6de7942","tid":1454258,"uid":300783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:50:33.000Z","msg":"長期黎講，同意!<br />\n<br />\n撤惡法<br />\n銷控罪<br />\n非暴動<br />\n查警暴<br />\n真普選"},{"pid":"e68ece9452954c22c44c3cb5a035895f35055545","tid":1454258,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:52:19.000Z","msg":"要同中共鬥長命<img src=\"/assets